===Noun===
{{wikipedia}}
'''baptism''' ([[uncountable]] and [[countable]]; plural: [[baptisms]])
# the [[Christian]] [[sacrament]] in which one is [[annointed]] with [[water]] and given a [[name]]
# a similar [[ceremony]] of [[initiation]], [[purification]] or [[naming]]

